file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Storage Space
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /storage-spaces/{storageSpaceName}/keys/{key}:
    get:
      summary: Get key value
      operationId: getKey
      parameters:
        - name: storageSpaceName
          in: path
          description: name of the storage space
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: key
          in: path
          description: name of the key to retrieve the value
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        200:
          description: successful operation
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
        400:
          description: Invalid key supplied
security:
  - authorization: []
components:
  securitySchemes:
    authorization:
      type: apiKey
      description: Represents API Key `authorization`
      name: Authorization
      in: header
